Repository: SPARXSTAR Platform Contracts
Authority: Starisian Technologies
Primary Maintainer: Max Barrett (@MaximillianGroup)

Scope
- Contracts under Contracts/ are governed artifacts synchronized from source service repositories.
- Repository automation, documentation, licensing, and governance files are managed in this repository.

Approval Expectations
- Contract changes require service-owner approval in the source repository and governance approval for breaking or material changes.
- Repository policy, licensing, and security-process changes require owner approval.

Escalation
- Security concerns follow SECURITY.md.
- Contribution and review expectations follow CONTRIBUTING.md.